					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Values of A, X, Y, P, and S are <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unspecified_behavior" class="postlink">unspecified</a> at power on except that bit 3 of P (I, interrupt priority) is 1 (allow NMI only), not 0 (allow NMI and IRQ).</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

